<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <div id="simple-calendar">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-3" id="previous-icon">
          <a href="/previous_month/<%= @count %>"><img src="/img/img1.png" class="previous-icon"></a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h1 class="month"><%= @month %>  <%= @starting_date.year %></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <a href="/next_month/<%= @count %>"><img src="/img/img2.png" class="next-icon"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th class="week-days">Su</th>
          <th class="week-days">Mo</th>
          <th class="week-days">Tu</th>
          <th class="week-days">We</th>
          <th class="week-days">Th</th>
          <th class="week-days">Fr</th>
          <th class="week-days">Sa</th>
        </tr>
        <% @simple_calendar.each do |week| %>
        <tr class="days">
          <% week.each do |day| %>
            <td class="matrix <%= day[1] %>"><a class = "day" href="/calendar/view/<%= day[0]%>"><%= day[0].day%></a></td>
          <% end %>
        </tr>
        <% end %>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="well col-md-4 links">
    <h2>Job Tracker</h2>
    <h4>
      Welcome to your job search and networking tool!
    </h4>
    <p>
      You can add tags/classifications to any contact, organization, or opening; and view you information by tag.<a href="/tags"> <em>Click here</em></a> to add tags!
    </p>
    <br>
    <p>
      You can save and classify all of your related contacts here- and associate them with organizations or particular job openings.<a href="/contacts"><em> Add a new contact.</em> </a>
    </p>
    <br>
    <p>
      Central to your any job search- the openings.<a href="/openings"><em> Add a new opening/job search,</em> </a>associate it with a company, add links and contacts, and track applications and interviews.
    </p>
    <br>
    <p>
      Keep track of all the companies and organizations you are applying to, or attending meet-ups with, here. Add links and associate contacts, job openings or events.
      <a href="/organizations"><em>Get started here.</em></a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
